Package org.jets3t.apps.uploader

Class Summary
AuthenticationDialog Dialog box for user to enter authentication information for NT or Basic authentication domains.
Uploader Dual application and applet for uploading files and XML metadata information to the Amazon S3 service.
UploaderFileExtensionFilter Defines which files can be selected within the Uploader's JFileChooser file chooser for upload to S3.
UserInputFields Manages the display of property-configured input fields in a panel, and collection of the user-entered results as properties.
XmlGenerator Generates XML documents containing metadata about files uploaded to Amazon S3 by the Uploader.
